test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -4225 == -65
 +  where -4225 = <built-in function prod>([-5, -13, -65])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x77353d312bc0>([-65])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x77353d312bc0> = [[1, -65], [1, -65, 1], [-65, 1], [-65, 1, -65], [1, -65], [1, -65, 1], ...].count
